  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Wealth creation through Pigeon Peas Value Chain(Malonda)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Christian Aid will work with ADAF to facilitate Savings for investment amongst cooperatives to carter for investments on production and marketing. Key to the investments will include input financing and the groups will be provided with financial literacy trainings to enable them properly transact.With increasing market participation, farmers will require access to a range of financial products and services to expand their engagement with markets. This is consistently identified as one of the most significant constraints on investment in improved agricultural production.</narrative>
  </description>
